  "markup": "Dr. Christopher Carraway of LTU interviews Gerry Ross, DDS - General Dentistry, Tottenham, Ontario at the NAALT/WALT joint meeting in Washington, DC, September 2014 on his uses of Low Level Laser for general dentistry in daily practice for pain and healing. Dr. Ross was a presenter on laser safety in the pre-conference sessions."
